Package com.alexgilleran.icesoap.request

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ListRequest<ResultType,SOAPFaultType>
    This request deals specifically with SOAP calls that recall a list of items, allowing listeners to be bound that will be called every time a new object is parsed rather than waiting until the entire request is finished.
    Request<ResultType,SOAPFaultType>
    Encapsulates all the code for making a SOAP Request - to use, create an object that implements the SOAP11Observer class (generally this is easiest using anonymous objects from the activity or fragment) and attach it using the Request#registerObserver(SOAP11Observer) method.
    RequestFactory
    Creates Requests, passing them a default, Apache HTTP Client based SOAPRequester implementation.
    Response
    Encapsulates the details of a response from an SOAP request.
    SOAP11ListRequest<ResultType>
    Extension of ListRequest that specifies a standard SOAP11Fault rather than specifying a specific one.
    SOAP11Request<ResultType>
    Encapsulates all the code for making a SOAP Request - to use, create an object that implements the SOAP11Observer class (generally this is easiest using anonymous objects from the activity or fragment) and attach it using the Request#registerObserver(SOAP11Observer) method.
    SOAPRequester
    Handles SOAP requests
